article_title: Myanmar's got a new exchange, but no stocks
article_text: Myanmar jumps the gun a little with its new stock exchange, opening with no stocks to trade, no approved underwriters, and securities laws barring foreign buying. Reuters' Martin Petty explains why authorities are even bothering with the bourse.
